N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 2396.13 - Rule of construction

State Regulations

The provisions of Parts 171 through 178 of this Title shall
apply to taxpayers participating in the program unless the provisions of this

Part are inconsistent therewith, in which case the provisions of this Part
shall govern. Notes
